data.description: Welcome to the enchanting charm of this farmhouse-style residence. From the moment you step onto the property, you'll be captivated by the inviting features that define this exceptional home. The picturesque wrap-around porch and white picket fence create an inviting ambiance. The beautifully eat-in kitchen features quartzite countertops, subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and elegant tile flooring. Built-in storage, glass-door cabinets, and a spacious island make this kitchen a true centerpiece. The generously sized living room allows for multiple seating areas, and the dining room easily accommodates gatherings. A converted closet serves as a combined mudroom and pantry, adjacent to a half bath. Original hardwood floors and ample windows flood the home with natural light. Upstairs, discover four inviting bedrooms, including a primary suite with an en suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. Abundant storage is found throughout, and a full bathroom completes the second floor. The finished basement space provides endless possibilities. Outside, a completely fenced area with a patio awaits your entertaining needs, and there's space for gardening. Solar panels enhance efficiency.Enjoy easy access to shopping, highways, local schools, and more. With 2,052 sqft of living space, and the added luxury of a sauna, this property seamlessly combines classic charm with modern amenities, making it a truly exceptional place to call home. Updates in 2020 include a new roof, gutters, and chimney.
